title: "Use FreeNX For Connecting Remotely"
date: 2015-09-24 19:08:09 +0800
comments: true
categories: Linux
---
### Installation
On ArchLinux, install it in AUR repository:    

```
$ yaourt -S nx-all
```

### Configuration
After installation, re-generate the keys for authorization:    

```
$ sudo /usr/NX/bin/nxserver --keygen
$ ls /usr/NX/share/keys/server.id_dsa.key 
/usr/NX/share/keys/server.id_dsa.key
# pwd
/usr/NX/home/nx/.ssh
# ls
authorized_keys2  default.id_dsa.pub  restore.id_dsa.pub
$ 
```
